{"tid":1882432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港珠澳大橋明起所有車輛免收通行費　至疫情防控工作結束","createTime":"2020-02-16T08:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T15:33:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a6dc10c11eed2a8adfe929de9107745327fefff1","tid":1882432,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/free-11_AyvSd_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffree-11_AyvSd_1200x0.png&h=876db1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，港府一直拒絕全面封關，另一方面港珠澳大橋多次延長小型客車免費通行優惠。港珠澳大橋管理局今日更進一步宣布，明日起所有車輛免收通行費，至疫情防控工作結束。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋管理局今日在微信發出公告，指根據相關政策，明日（17日）零時起至疫情防控工作結束，對依法通行港珠澳大橋的所有車輛免收通行費，新政策的具體截止時間另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n今年 1 月港珠澳大橋管理局已宣佈在春節假期免收7座及以下小型客車通行費，原訂優惠時間至 1 月 30 日結束。不過管理局之後兩度將優惠時間延長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B%E5%85%8D%E6%94%B6%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E8%B2%BB-%E8%87%B3%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BC%259B%25E5%2585%258D%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259D%259F%2F&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=42c7c8d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BC%259B%25E5%